OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FEverything is going far too well
OL,7,     Fon the week's final visit, to Gary
OL,8,     Fand Chris's place - The Grays
OL,9,     FHotel in Blackpool. So naturally,
OL,10,     Fthe B&Bers root out some issues at
OL,11,     Fbreakfast.
OL,12,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FTension abounds on payment day,
OL,14,     Fwith a number of suspiciously low
OL,15,     Fscores on the agenda. Who'll
OL,16,     Femerge from the vitriol
OL,17,     Fvictorious?
